09:15.800 --> 09:16.810
Perkins, who knows?

09:17.010 --> 09:18.350
Sweet gap, though, huh? Nice teeth.

09:18.550 --> 09:21.480
What we're gonna do
is we're gonna focus on

09:21.680 --> 09:25.730
