09:41.260 --> 09:42.270
Come on, fellas.

09:42.470 --> 09:46.190
What about Lancaster Gordon? Anybody?

09:46.390 --> 09:47.440
Louisville.

09:47.640 --> 09:49.980
Louisville. He went to Louisville, Bill.

09:50.180 --> 09:51.900
That is correct. I wrote it right there.

09:52.090 --> 09:53.310
How about-- What do we think
about Charles Barkley,

09:53.510 --> 09:54.400
