- SONNY: Hey, Rob.

11:30.640 --> 11:33.310
STRASSER: Hey, Sonny, wh--
honestly, what the fuck is your problem?

11:33.510 --> 11:35.060
- Who are we gonna get?
- (urinating)

11:35.260 --> 11:37.060
