(phone ringing)

01:26:13.500 --> 01:26:14.770
Hello, Falk.

01:26:14.970 --> 01:26:15.980
DELORIS (over phone):
Mr. Vaccaro.

01:26:16.180 --> 01:26:18.900
Mrs. Jordan.

01:26:19.090 --> 01:26:20.870
I have some news for you.

01:26:22.080 --> 01:26:23.580
