01:32:56.680 --> 01:32:58.600
Jesus Christ.

01:32:58.800 --> 01:33:00.400
(sighs)

01:33:00.590 --> 01:33:02.080
I'm really sorry.

01:33:06.040 --> 01:33:07.580
(sighs)

