01:33:17.090 --> 01:33:19.150
Well, of course I do.

01:33:19.340 --> 01:33:21.150
There's not a lot of point
in having a basketball guru

01:33:21.340 --> 01:33:22.480
if you don't listen to what he has to say.

01:33:22.680 --> 01:33:23.980
The board's never gonna do that.

01:33:24.180 --> 01:33:25.230
This has never happened before.

01:33:25.430 --> 01:33:26.520
(Sonny stammers)

01:33:26.720 --> 01:33:28.150
