I paid Carolyn Davidson
$35 for that design in 1971.

01:40:30.510 --> 01:40:32.810
- I heard you didn't like it.
- No.

01:40:33.010 --> 01:40:34.700
I said it would grow on me.

01:40:36.080 --> 01:40:37.910
Well, maybe it will.

01:40:41.370 --> 01:40:43.290
(sighs)

01:40:45.410 --> 01:40:46.580
Hey, Phil.

01:40:48.700 --> 01:40:51.350
