01:40:53.720 --> 01:40:55.500
I appreciate it.

01:40:57.950 --> 01:40:59.600
You're a brilliant guy, Sonny.

01:40:59.800 --> 01:41:02.270
And you have courage.

01:41:02.470 --> 01:41:04.450
